metadata.name: Fog and Tea
metadata.description:
And the poet said:

Did the moisture of the night fall into your eyes?
Please don't look wet.
Let your hair down, tell me your problem.
Just don't look wet..

It was one of the days when I went out for a photo shoot again. After taking pictures all day long I decided to go back. All of a sudden the fog covered the whole place and I saw the place where I took the photo. The light came on in my head. I took the car in the back and turned on the headlights from afar. And the result…

Artist :Murat İbranoğlu
Camera: Canon EOS 5D Mark III
Dimensions: 4217*2811
Resolution: 300dpi
Location: Kocaeli/ Türkiye
Date: 04.09.2016
Edition: 1/1
